{"tid":2100921,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友已經失業左勁耐","createTime":"2020-07-09T11:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T02:18:17.000Z","uid":35361,"like":4,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0957c07693c6cf7ad896b485e99107f01f7a714f","tid":2100921,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:34:59.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊左已經4個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係一齊之前已經知佢未搵倒工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日食屋企遊手好閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開頭叫過佢去是但搵份part time賺下生活費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼減輕下佢屋企經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲唔使永遠出街都我出錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(連爆房錢condom錢都係我出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n次次見佢咁頹廢就叫佢認真d搵份工返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講多兩講就燥左屌返我轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依加佢已經半年冇返過工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日去爆房都係我出錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時都係佢插我先 俾佢出左野enjoy左先到我既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最終我今日真係好嬲 我撳住佢插佢出左野就走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6945c6f904bb3d694b44145b21e486936f43458b","tid":2100921,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:41:03.000Z","msg":"一向都係有個男人養頭家架啦<br />\n你咪當養埋另外一個男人囉"},{"pid":"42b5ef343dbee5fde69a6e5d1373ba1148881551","tid":2100921,"uid":326758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:42:09.000Z","msg":"樓下係戇鳩仔"},{"pid":"c3af21e4dae4773a650259d70974f68b5020ddcf","tid":2100921,"uid":116827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:42:19.000Z","msg":"Gay"},{"pid":"4665d1d909ca24ec82107552ae2b3367fa8d7c12","tid":2100921,"uid":119135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:48:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">THIS</span></span>"},{"pid":"19a9d7a77b449390e551fe8df3784981f88d5935","tid":2100921,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:19:09.000Z","msg":"真人真事"},{"pid":"65cd8c37ef74ba2f080aba914024cc8197f6a1b2","tid":2100921,"uid":6136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:39:59.000Z","msg":"你係男人出錢有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77c22126624aef7cd8b97f49740241f3ddacc2e","tid":2100921,"uid":54177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:42:24.000Z","msg":"男人出condom錢有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43593b986096131ac8381ef4c1ec31081c8e3580","tid":2100921,"uid":308732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T13:01:23.000Z","msg":"你地同一個男朋友？"},{"pid":"93f5a9729377c55d539c7c5d68d18572f2e68595","tid":2100921,"uid":35361,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"65cd8c37ef74ba2f080aba914024cc8197f6a1b2","tid":2100921,"uid":6136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:39:59.000Z","msg":"你係男人出錢有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T13:53:02.000Z","msg":"佢都係男人"},{"pid":"751e03214775122148b2321d43b25d8fd8ebe97d","tid":2100921,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:36:53.000Z","msg":"😂😂😂"},{"pid":"f1141372e8e60229ec4b92c954c76bc6416395fd","tid":2100921,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:39:2